title: 'Dora the Explorer' Live-Action Movie Happening at Paramount
text:
Published By: MovieWeb.com: Movie News - Today 
'Puss in Boots' scribe Tom Wheeler has been set to write both 'Dora the Explorer' and 'Micronauts' movies for Paramount Pictures....
